data.description: Welcome to this spacious townhouse in the beautiful Happy Valley.   The main level features an open floor plan with a granite island & an eating bar that flows into the dining room & great room with an electric fireplace. The balcony off the living room provides an abundance of light and air. Upstairs, the vaulted primary suite is generously sized w/walk-in closet & on-suite bath. Laundry conveniently located upstairs with 3 bedrooms. The huge lower level can be a 4th bedroom, bonus room, or office that opens to a large two-car garage. A prime location that offers privacy and territorial views. Near Happy Valley restaurants, shopping, schools, coffee shops, and a community park.
